data.title: California's Luxury Dude Ranch
data.meta_description: With over 10,500 private acres to explore, Alisal Ranch offers a luxury, California dude ranch experience just outside Solvang, CA. Enjoy a simple life, well-lived.
data.text:
Located in the heart of Santa Barbara Wine Country, Alisal Ranch offers guests a modern taste of the old west. Under the open sky, our 10,500 acres provide endless inspiration for family-driven adventures, romantic getaways, special events, and more. We invite you to learn about the history of this timeless place, then get ready to unwind and embrace your own sense of wanderlust.

Our ranch accommodations were designed with western luxury in mind. A place to get away and escape city life, with the quiet of the countryside offering a peaceful oasis to relax in after a day of adventure. We have spaces for every type of guest from charming suites to our ranch houses offering accommodations for up to 10 people.

Our respect for the land—paired with a passion for Western hospitality—means you can expect local, bountiful, and delicious food here at Alisal Ranch. Think: the best of California cuisine, prepared to pay homage to the traditions of ranch-style cooking. Our chefs are eager to surprise and delight you.

At Alisal Ranch, we start each day with an unrelenting curiosity—and we invite you to do the same. There’s no better place to connect with the passionate, pioneering spirit, or to spend meaningful moments with friends and family. Take the road less traveled, breathe a little deeper, feel the power of nature, and dream under the stars.
